{"tid":1351631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「光復香港 時代革命」，試著說「光復香港 革命獨立」","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:27:23.000Z","uid":192971,"like":11,"dislike":153,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b467ed66503df69d0b4c3f6abfbfc190f50f36bd","tid":1351631,"uid":192971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"多一日比共匪管治 就多一日比共匪魚肉<br />\n要建立屬於香港人既香港，首先要潛移默化，口號要傳銷洗腦式地入屋<br />\n一切由連登做起！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 革命獨立 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a61c616d1fd5d8a0d55c80fb3b71cc9f673228ed","tid":1351631,"uid":192971,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港 革命獨立 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee186d0c11603d72ca333f79d6c0838483b95b70","tid":1351631,"uid":61853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e241cf0f9e6a4ab3838f0705d24c16209ee60d33","tid":1351631,"uid":192971,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港 革命獨立 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea45ee0bd8d4e51add84b19bbefda9d028aea60","tid":1351631,"uid":192971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:00:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港 革命獨立 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedf2a264f414fd1300ecca79d9850835a2e5ced","tid":1351631,"uid":192971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:02:28.000Z