e1dc91b2c739063520bd9f281aa1b69fa4","tid":1351631,"uid":81628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb43270503f38c13cd60d020ebc305373019daf4","tid":1351631,"uid":192971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"558a4bb75579c9eac371c298aaea3efc46494666","tid":1351631,"uid":81628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa3d1ee1a2335a3bbc1391cbc2e0daaa4aa8115","tid":1351631,"uid":192971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"比人負皮到唔想再推呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔明白未? 要完全脫離共產黨先會有出路?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dosQGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dosQGS</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"sor你比網軍大量負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"我可以點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"兄弟唔洗灰心<br />\n你有的是時間，開一個post唔夠咪開第二個，你唔係以為開一個post就夠啊<br />\n佢地夠膽負你皮，你咪有幾多開幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f8d3251392ea57d0fadada8ace7aff4327afa5","tid":1351631,"uid":276471,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"又帶風向去港獨，負評，block user"},{"pid":"5f0eadc2c7029671b913a0add0433fe9d9ed567e","tid":1351631,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"光復革命 香港獨立會好啲"},{"pid":"e3ae01bb1716a8b9af8554dd6e20b95f90e2bdd3","tid":1351631,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"From Simon Lui (Facebook)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156060495911105%26set%3Da.45435071104%26type%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=cd50e583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我經歷過波士頓馬拉松爆炸案，明白襲擊後的恐怖<br />\n1) 爆炸前30分鐘，我仍在Boylston st現場，只是早走了<br />\n2) MIT校警就在我Lab樓下(Building 32)被槍殺，只是我偷懶無返工(偷懶萬歲)<br />\n<br />\n我嗰晚好驚，本來諗住「一星期唔出街，以後見人都要提防」... 但原來我錯了<br />\n<br />\n【恐佈分子的目的，不是要讓100人死掉，而是要令幾億人害怕】<br />\n<br />\n是波士頓人教曉我，面對恐懼就要更勇敢。因為爆炸後第二晚，波士頓人竟然這樣：<br />\n- 不躲在家中，照常出街跑步<br />\n- 不讓恐懼擴散，反而故意外出食飯購物<br />\n- 人與人之間的信任沒有動搖。反而整網頁讓居民登記，開放自己家，讓因爆炸案錯過火車的旅人住一晚 <br />\n<br />\n「開放自己家！黐線㗎！引狼入室！」不是的<br />\n- 若恐佈分子要襲擊，點會無方法？<br />\n- 由華盛頓來旅行但錯過火車嘅自己人，點會睇唔出？幫佢點會有事？<br />\n- 自己人互相幫助，其實安全得很<br />\n- 所以最後，我自己都踩單車出去飲咖啡，重買水比站崗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n恐佈分子的失敗，在於居民鎮定不害怕，在於鄰里關係沒有動搖。若要防範恐佈分子，不是要人人自危，而是要把問題源頭清掉吧。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，守望相助，不要落單，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}